# Input

```md
[hello][world]

[hello][]

[hello]

[  spaced  ][  label  ]

[*foo* bar][]

[foo][BaR]

text with [inline][ref] in the middle

[link with **bold**][ref]

```


# Formatted

```md
[hello][world]

[hello][]

[hello]

[  spaced  ][  label  ]

[_foo_ bar][]

[foo][BaR]

text with [inline][ref] in the middle

[link with **bold**][ref]

```
